WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:06.849
Can I talk to you real quick?

2
00:00:06.849 --> 00:00:07.849
What are you doing here?

3
00:00:07.849 --> 00:00:09.849
This isn't about my allowance.

4
00:00:09.849 --> 00:00:10.849
I don't want it.

5
00:00:10.849 --> 00:00:14.849
I just want me and my children to spend our birthday together.

6
00:00:14.849 --> 00:00:16.850
Surely you can understand that.

7
00:00:16.850 --> 00:00:26.339
You expected me to believe that?

8
00:00:26.339 --> 00:00:31.339
In the past, but I want to make it right for you and our children.

9
00:00:31.339 --> 00:00:34.070
You are a terrible mother.

10
00:00:34.070 --> 00:00:36.070
You need to leave my wife alone.

11
00:00:36.070 --> 00:00:41.000
Otherwise, I'll send you overseas.

12
00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:42.509
No.

13
00:00:42.509 --> 00:00:44.609
Do you want worse?

14
00:00:44.609 --> 00:00:46.609
I'll send you to New Jersey.

